    "tabs_JcVwYg": {
      "type": "tabs",
      "blocks": {
        "tab_cAFn4M": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "White Rice or Black Rice?",
            "content": "<h3>Choose Your Peel Shot</h3><p><strong>- White Rice</strong><br/><br/>For sensitive, normal, or dry skin.<br/><br/>Gentle, hydrating exfoliation that delivers instant glow, refines skin texture, boosts hydration, and is safe for sensitive skin.<br/><br/><strong>Use:</strong> 2–3 times per week.</p><p><strong>- Black Rice</strong><br/><br/>For oily, combination, or blemish-prone skin.<br/><br/>Intensive, purifying exfoliation that deeply cleans pores, helps reduce blackheads, controls excess oil, and minimizes the look of enlarged pores.<br/><br/><strong>Use:</strong> 1–2 times per week (focus on problem areas).</p><p><strong>Our tip:</strong><br/><br/>Not sure which one to choose? Start with <strong>White Rice</strong> for sensitive or normal skin. Choose <strong>Black Rice</strong> if you struggle with enlarged pores or excess oil. You can also alternate between both depending on your skin’s needs.</p><p><strong>Recommended use:</strong> 2–3 times per week</p><h3>Peel Shot Black Rice</h3><p><strong>Best for:</strong> Oily, combination, or blemish-prone skin</p><p><strong>Action:</strong> Intensive, purifying exfoliation</p><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>Deep pore cleansing<br/></li><li>Helps reduce blackheads and impurities<br/></li><li>Sebum control<br/></li><li>Minimizes the appearance of enlarged pores<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Recommended use:</strong> 1–2 times per week (focus on problem areas)</p><h3>Our Recommendation</h3><p>Not sure which one to choose?<br/><br/>Start with <strong>White Rice</strong> if you have sensitive or normal skin.<br/><br/>Choose <strong>Black Rice</strong> if you’re dealing with enlarged pores or excess oil.</p><p><strong>Pro tip:</strong> You can also alternate between the two depending on your skin’s needs!</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "tab_TxFwiR": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How to Use the Peel Shot ?",
            "content": "<h3>It’s Ultra-Simple in 3 Steps</h3><ol><li>Cleanse your face and dry it completely<br/></li><li>Apply a small amount to dry skin and gently massage in circular motions for 1–2 minutes<br/><em>(you’ll see the little flakes — that’s dead skin being removed!)</em><br/></li><li>Rinse with lukewarm water and follow with your moisturizer<br/></li></ol><p><strong>Frequency:</strong> Use 2–3 times per week maximum. Avoid over-exfoliating to prevent skin irritation.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "tab_qih8hJ": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is the Peel Shot suitable for my skin?",
            "content": "<p>Yes! The Peel Shot is suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin. </p><p>Choose <strong>White Rice</strong> for sensitive, normal, or dry skin with ultra-gentle exfoliation, or <strong>Black Rice</strong> for normal to oily or blemish-prone skin with a more powerful, purifying action. If you’re unsure, start with the White Rice version and test on a small area first. </p><p>If you have very sensitive skin or a skin condition, we recommend consulting your dermatologist before use.<br/><br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "tab_fjmRgM": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Free Delivery & 30-Day Guarantee ✅",
            "content": "<p><strong>Home delivery is free.</strong> Depending on order volume, estimated delivery time is <strong>6–11 business days </strong></p><p>You have <strong>30 days to change your mind after receiving your order</strong>.<br/><br/><br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
